Cartalyst Developer License purchases allows a single “live” installation in a production environment and ancillary “development use only” installations as needed to support the live installation (such as development and staging servers).

Cartalyst Studio License purchases allow multiple “live” installation in a production environment and ancillary “development use only” installations as needed to support the live installation (such as development and staging servers). Studio installations do not require additional license purchases. If you have specific installation needs not covered by this license, please contact us.

