Studio License: Holders of the Studio License may use the Software as if they had the Developer license. In addition, the Studio License holders are allowed to integrate Cartalyst Software with intranet websites and public web services, develop their own products based on or containing Cartalyst Extensions. However, neither license holder nor license holder’s clients can sell Cartalyst Extensions as a sole product (with or without modification); License holder and license holder’s clients should use it fairly; we still hold all the rights for Cartalyst code, and we solely determine “fair use” of Cartalyst Software.  Studio License holders may expect priority response to their support requests and the highest quality of service and support, including but not limited to: help with installation of the Software, phone, Skype or other live consultations, etc. Support for the holders of the Studio License is limited to one year from the date of purchase.

